title: Feed Drop: May I Elaborate: Daily Wisdom from JB Smoove
description: It's a feed drop Con-gregation! Check out a new Team Coco podcast called May I Elaborate: Daily Wisdom from JB Smoove. Every morning, JB breaks down an inspirational quote, like only he can, to help you achieve your highest potential. Plus, he’s not even asking for money! So, enjoy the show and Stay Schemin!
author: rss@earwolf.com (Earwolf & Laci Mosley)
